        "TileImage": "$($repository 006e46cf-afb8-47af-bd88-905d574c6e8b).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening agent\r\ryour target is Shanon Reed, an agent who was recruited by us two years ago. Reed was planted in Biological Warfare Section 12  that belongs to our opponents. We found out that Reed was compromised and later turned by the opposition into a double agent. She has provided them with sensitive information that cost us a valuable agent that was arrested two days ago.  your mission is to eliminate her and exfil without being detected or leaving any trace behind.\r\rGood luck agent",
